
src/            C code & project files
BUILD           Build and compile instructions
cpcfs.cfg       Startup commands for CPCFS
cpcfs.doc       Documentation for everything
cpcfs.hlp       Online helpfile
drop_tag.bat    Removing timestamp from image (for CPE)
FILES           List of files
getcpm.bas      Loco Basic program to read CP/M Tracks
LICENSE         BSD-2-Clause License
README.md       Project overview
template.doc    Template for the documatation
VERSION-*       indicate current version

src/cpcfs.c         the main sourcecode
src/cpcfs.h         some prototypes, constants, includes, and so on
src/dos.h       Windows specific header
src/dos.c       Windows specific routines
src/fs.c        routines for manipulating the filesystem
src/Makefile    Unix Makefile
src/Makefile.bcc C++ Builder CLI Makefile
src/match.c     some routines realising regular expression matching for CP/M wildcards
src/match.h     header for regular expressions
src/makedoc.c   merge cpcfs.hlp and template.doc to cpcfs.doc
src/tools.c     general routines for CPCFS
src/ui.c        routines for the user interface
src/unix.h      Unix specific header
src/unix.c      unix specific routines
